
'''Zambia Super League ya mu 2021–22''' ndi nyengo ya 61 ya [[Zambian Super League|Zambia Super League]], ligi yampikisano wapamwamba kwambiri ku Zambia. Ligi ikuyembekezeka kuyamba pa 11 Seputembala. ZESCO United ndiomwe ikuteteza, itapambana chikho chachisanu ndi chinayi cha Super League munyengo yapitayi. 

